edu.mhs.compsys.idt

Class StateTransition

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.mhs.compsys.idt.StateTransition

  • public class StateTransition
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a container for the Transition between two states. It consists of two strings, the name of the two states, and an ArrayList of Changes.
